      "description": "中文\r\n\r\nLooki Sync 1.0.5\r\n修复\r\n兼容旧版本 Obsidian：将创建文件夹所用的方法从较新的 createFolder 改为更稳定、兼容性更好的 adapter.mkdir，避免在不满足最低版本要求的 Obsidian 上触发\"使用了新版本 API\"的报错。\r\n清理构建警告：移除了未使用的异常变量，让代码更干净、通过官方校验。\r\nEnglish\r\n\r\nLooki Sync 1.0.5\r\nFixed\r\nCompatibility with older Obsidian: Replaced the newer createFolder call with the more stable adapter.mkdir when creating folders, fixing the \"uses APIs newer than the declared minAppVersion\" check on older Obsidian versions.\r\nCleaner build: Removed an unused exception variable to eliminate the lint warning and pass validatio",
