      "author": "kidd911-cmd",
      "description": "Looki Sync 1.0.4\r\n修复\r\n自动创建目录：同步前会自动创建笔记目录与媒体子目录，不再需要手动提前建好文件夹（修复了目标文件夹不存在时报错的问题）。\r\n图片现在能正常显示了：之前所有图片被强制保存为 .jpg，但 Looki 返回的图片实际可能是 png / webp / heic 等格式，导致 Obsidian 无法显示。现在会按真实格式保存，图片可正常预览。\r\n区分图片与视频：笔记里的媒体嵌入现在带图标标识——🖼️ 图片、🎬 视频，一眼就能分清。\r\nEnglish\r\n\r\nLooki Sync 1.0.4\r\nFixed\r\nAuto-create folders: The plugin now creates the notes folder and media subfolders automatically before syncing, so you no longer need to create them manually (fixes the error when the target folder did not exist).\r\nImages now display correctly: Previously all images were forced to save as .jpg, but Looki may return png / webp / heic, etc., which made them unviewable in Obsidian. They are now saved with their real format and render properly.\r\nDistinguish images from videos: Media embeds in notes are now labeled with icons — 🖼️ for images and 🎬 for videos — so they are easy to tell apart.",
